	<h1 id="firstHeading" class="firstHeading" lang="en">Proto-Indo-European mythology</h1>
	
	<div id="bodyContent" class="mw-body-content">
		<div id="siteSub" class="noprint">From Wikipedia, the free encyclopedia</div>
		<div id="contentSub"><span class="mw-redirectedfrom">&#160;&#160;(Redirected from <a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=Proto-Indo-European_religion&amp;redirect=no" class="mw-redirect" title="Proto-Indo-European religion">Proto-Indo-European religion</a>)</span></div>
		
		
		<div id="jump-to-nav"></div>
		<a class="mw-jump-link" href="Proto-Indo-European_religion#mw-head">Jump to navigation</a>
		<a class="mw-jump-link" href="Proto-Indo-European_religion#p-search">Jump to search</a>
		<div id="mw-content-text" lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr"><div class="mw-parser-output"><div class="shortdescription nomobile noexcerpt noprint searchaux" style="display:none">Body of myths and stories attributed to the Proto-Indo-Europeans</div>
<div class="thumb tright"><div class="thumbinner" style="width:252px;"><a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/File:Solvognen-00100.jpg" class="image"><img alt="" src="http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/e/e1/Solvognen-00100.jpg/250px-Solvognen-00100.jpg" decoding="async" width="250" height="187" class="thumbimage" srcset="http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/e/e1/Solvognen-00100.jpg/375px-Solvognen-00100.jpg 1.5x, http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/e/e1/Solvognen-00100.jpg/500px-Solvognen-00100.jpg 2x" data-file-width="6088" data-file-height="4550" /></a>  <div class="thumbcaption"><div class="magnify"><a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/File:Solvognen-00100.jpg" class="internal" title="Enlarge"></a></div><a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Trundholm_sun_chariot" title="Trundholm sun chariot">Trundholm sun chariot</a> pictured, <a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Nordic_Bronze_Age" title="Nordic Bronze Age">Nordic Bronze Age</a>, c. 1600 BC</div></div></div>
